End Function


Print All Courses:
Function printAllCoursesHash(hashTable)

    Create empty list

    Loop through all buckets
        Add courses to list

    Sort list

    Print all courses

End Function


Search One Course:
Function searchCourseHash(hashTable, courseNumber)

    Find bucket using hash

    Loop through bucket
